# S2-3: Content Moderation Flow

Add flagging/reporting for turns and logs, a moderator review queue, and hide/close actions.

> **Note on auth:** S2-1 (JWT) is in review but not yet merged. Reports use the **session token** as reporter identity (already exists). The moderator endpoints are gated by `ADMIN_SECRET` env var via a header — upgradeable to role-based JWT once S2-1 merges.

